Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,苏珊娜\N{\fs12}Suzanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我跟尼克同居了\N{\fs12}You knew I was living with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你知不知道我怀孕了\N{\fs12}Did you know that I was pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你知不知道尼克正在缓刑期\N{\fs12}Did you know that Nick's on probation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他被抓到嗑药或者酗酒的话  他有可能会被关进监狱的\N{\fs12}That if he gets caught with drugs or drinking that he will go to jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不知道  - 你不知道吗\N{\fs12}- No. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那好  下次你见到他的时候请你告诉他\N{\fs12}Okay. Well, you just please tell him the next time you see him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经造成了很多伤害\N{\fs12}that he's done enough harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再收拾他的烂摊子了  请一定转告他\N{\fs12}And I'm tired of cleaning up his messes. You can just tell him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟他讲  让他4点一定要感到法院  否则我就给他的缓刑官打电话了\N{\fs12}And you tell him to show up at the court at 4:OO or I will call his probation officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  他不在家\N{\fs12}Burton, he's not home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我问过他的秘书了  也问过格雷琴  没人知道他去哪儿了\N{\fs12}I spoke to his secretary and to Gretchen, and no one knows where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs12}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs12}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,放桌上吧\N{\fs12}Just, uh, put them on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  我想我可以在几个小时内汇总一下意见书\N{\fs12}Look, I think I can pull together an opinion Ietter in a couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是合并需要的所有的文件  章程  宪章  诉讼  所有的文件\N{\fs12}This is everything from the merger: bylaws, charter, lawsuits, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,给我几个小时  我来看一下  好吗\N{\fs12}So give me a couple of hours to go through this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以在几小时内写一份意见信吗\N{\fs12}You can draft an opinion letter in a couple of hours, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个很棒的律师  伯顿  我看可以的\N{\fs12}I'm a pretty good lawyer, Burton. I think I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,给\N{\fs12}Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来不错\N{\fs12}Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃吧\N{\fs12}You can eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你不吃吗\N{\fs12}You're not hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  遗嘱的事情\N{\fs12}So, a living will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,遗嘱里会写你希望正常自然地死亡\N{\fs12}A living will says that you desire to die a natural death,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,并且不希望用医疗设备或者急救措施来维持生命\N{\fs12}and you don't want to be kept alive by medical treatment or heroic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}That's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  所以\N{\fs12}Right. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这份声明写着你心智健全\N{\fs12}This basically states that you are of sound mind
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,且是自愿提出这个声明的\N{\fs12}and that you are voluntarily making this declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你示意主治医生不再维持生命\N{\fs12}That you direct the attending physician to withhold or withdraw life support.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  还有几个具体的问题\N{\fs12}Then there are specific questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管问吧\N{\fs12}Fire away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你想不想进行心脏复苏\N{\fs12}Do you want cardio-pulmonary resuscitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不想\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你想不想机械设备来维持呼吸\N{\fs12}Do you want mechanical respiration?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不想\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还有哪些  你说\N{\fs12}Just do the whole list, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,管饲  输血  手术  透析  抗生素\N{\fs12}Tube feeding, blood transfusions, surgery, dialysis, antibiotics.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要  不要  不要  都写不要\N{\fs12}No. No. No to all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想要捐赠器官吗  - 如果我的器官还能用的话\N{\fs12}- Do you wish to donate any organs? - If they're useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  妈妈  - 嗨  亲爱的\N{\fs12}- Hey, Mom. - Hi, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我有好多作业\N{\fs12}I have a lot of homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他很认真\N{\fs12}He's so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不看电视  也没有几个朋友  每天一回来就做作业\N{\fs12}No TV. Not many friends. Just does his school work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,每门成绩都是A\N{\fs12}Straight As.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,其他妈妈都很羡慕我  都希望能有这样的孩子\N{\fs12}The other moms, they wish their kid was just like mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  我不想这样  我宁愿他考个C  能时不时笑一笑\N{\fs12}but, I don't know, I just wish he'd get a C and smile once in awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小男子汉\N{\fs12}My little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  亨德里克斯小姐  你在这边坐得还舒服吗\N{\fs12}Hi, Miss Hendricks. How's your sit-in going?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,需不需要去趟洗手间\N{\fs12}Need to use the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,露露  我不是有意\N{\fs12}Lulu, uh, I don't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有人见过尼克吗\N{\fs12}Has anybody actually spoken to Nick today?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要不要担心\N{\fs12}Should we be concerned?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.47,0:22:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  我是路易莎·阿切尔\N{\fs12}Louisa Archer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.02,0:22:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢你  罗斯玛丽  谢谢\N{\fs12}All right, thank you, Rosemarie. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才是你的缓刑官打来的\N{\fs12}That was your probation officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在要在法院见我们\N{\fs12}She's gonna meet us at the courthouse right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.89,0:22:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,关键是你的手要很放松\N{\fs12}lt's important to keep your hand really relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要很灵活\N{\fs12}You gotta be limber.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  露露  - 嗨 伯顿\N{\fs12}- Hey, Lulu. - Hi, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.10,0:22:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我在找尼克  - 我也是\N{\fs12}- I'm looking for Nick. - Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有给他家里打电话\N{\fs12}Have you tried calling him at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有  打过了  我甚至叫杰克去他家看过了  但是\N{\fs12}Yeah, I did. Even had Jake go over there but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  他有可能\N{\fs12}Well, he's probably--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们都知道他去干嘛了\N{\fs12}I think we both know\N{\fs12}what he's probably doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.12,0:23:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  阿尔文  - 嗨  伯顿\N{\fs12}- Hey, Alvin. - Hey, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.59,0:23:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你介意我去尼克的办公室看看吗  我在找一本法律意见书\N{\fs12}Do you mind if I check out Nick's office? I'm looking for a legal opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.14,0:23:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不介意  进去吧  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- No, go right ahead. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.53,0:23:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,关于你儿子的监护权\N{\fs12}As for the custody of your son...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不会很容易  - 好吧\N{\fs12}- It's not gonna be easy. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.31,0:23:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,按照宾夕法尼亚州的关于亲生父母的法律规定\N{\fs12}Presumption in Pennsylvania is for the biological parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.73,0:23:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.76,0:23:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么意思\N{\fs12}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你的前夫有权决定孩子去哪里\N{\fs12}Your ex-husband has the legal right to contest the placement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  还是有其他办法的吧\N{\fs12}But there is a way?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  有个规定叫备用监护人法案\N{\fs12}Yes, there's something called the Standby Guardian Act.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的  你真的很在行\N{\fs12}You're really... You're so good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的很聪明\N{\fs12}You're really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.49,0:23:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  备用监护人法案\N{\fs12}So, the Standby Guardian Act.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.89,0:23:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这个法案允许身患绝症的父母做出监护权的决定\N{\fs12}It allows a terminally ill parent to commence a custody action
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,断定另一位家长无法照顾这个孩子\N{\fs12}that alleges that the other parent is unable to care for their child.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以试着指定一个新的监护人\N{\fs12}You could try to designate a new guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我猜你不会赢\N{\fs12}My guess is you will lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.28,0:24:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.01,0:24:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我说他爸爸并没有虐待或者冷落孩子\N{\fs12}From what you've told me of your son's father, he's not abusive or neglectful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.28,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是一个好爸爸  他不爱孩子\N{\fs12}Well, he's not a good father. He's not loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,法律上没有关于爱的规定\N{\fs12}Legally ''loving'' is not a requirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  是的\N{\fs12}Right. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.18,0:24:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有考虑问下你的儿子他想怎么做\N{\fs12}Have you considered asking your son what he wants to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.47,0:24:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他还只是个孩子\N{\fs12}Oh, he's just a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.95,0:24:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我需要给他制定一个切实可行的计划\N{\fs12}No. I need to come up with a solid plan for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.44,0:24:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,给他制定切实可行的计划吗\N{\fs12}A solid plan for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.33,0:24:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.54,0:24:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要问问他  他想做什么\N{\fs12}You need to ask him what he wants to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.01,0:24:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他还只是个孩子\N{\fs12}He's just a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.47,0:24:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我能不能用下洗手间\N{\fs12}ls there a bathroom I might use?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.27,0:24:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,楼上  走廊的尽头\N{\fs12}Upstairs, end of the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.14,0:26:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  杰瑞  - 嗨  阿尔文\N{\fs12}- Hi, Jerry. - Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.87,0:26:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你认识尼克·法林吗  - 认识\N{\fs12}- You know Nick Fallin? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.28,0:26:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 今天有见到他吗  - 没有\N{\fs12}- Seen him around today? - Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.59,0:26:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果今天见到他  能不能打电话通知我一声\N{\fs12}Oh, uh, if you see him, would you give me a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.69,0:26:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然  - 谢谢\N{\fs12}- Sure. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.37,0:26:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有消息了吗\N{\fs12}Any word yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.75,0:26:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有\N{\fs12}Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.04,0:26:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我必须进去了  告诉客户们事情的真相\N{\fs12}Well, I'm gonna have to go in there and... tell the clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.01,0:26:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我快好了\N{\fs12}I'm--I'm almost finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.99,0:26:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你不可能分析出风险和负债的\N{\fs12}You couldn't have analyzed the risks and liabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.51,0:26:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,已经足够了\N{\fs12}lt's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.33,0:26:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  我不能\N{\fs12}Well, I can't go in--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.09,0:26:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  如果你弄错了  我们会被起诉\N{\fs12}I mean, if you're wrong, we get sued.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.23,0:26:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,伯顿  如果不去  我们还是会被起诉的\N{\fs12}Burton, we're gonna get sued either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.81,0:26:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不  这不是我的办事风格\N{\fs12}Nah, I don't do business like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.33,0:26:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  相信我伯顿  这也不是我的办事风格\N{\fs12}What? Believe me, Burton, I don't do business like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.43,0:26:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是  我现在只是在弥补尼克的\N{\fs12}I mean, I'm just trying to cover Nick--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.65,0:26:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有进他的房子\N{\fs12}Did you go inside the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.09,0:26:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.66,0:26:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\fs12}Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.06,0:26:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  去他的房子  如果需要撬开\N{\fs12}Look, go back over there, and if you have to break--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.94,0:27:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,花盆下面有一把钥匙\N{\fs12}There's a key underneath the planter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.61,0:27:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,去办公室把那封意见信找出来\N{\fs12}Go inside the house and find the damn letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.38,0:27:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做会更好\N{\fs12}It would be better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.95,0:27:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好个屁\N{\fs12}Like hell it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.33,0:27:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是希望他待在爱他的人的身边\N{\fs12}I just want him to be around someone who loves him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.31,0:27:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你听听你自己的话  你在说什么\N{\fs12}What are you saying? Listen to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.69,0:27:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直醉心工作  而且你很容易愤怒\N{\fs12}You work all the time and you're so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.74,0:27:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮  拜托\N{\fs12}Anne, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.18,0:27:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望孩子跟我在一起  他是我的儿子\N{\fs12}This is what I want. He is my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.87,0:27:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不会放弃他的  我不会把他送给别人的\N{\fs12}I will never, never give him up, never give him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.98,0:27:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白吗\N{\fs12}You understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.72,0:27:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有在听我说话  你没有在听\N{\fs12}You are not hearing me. You're not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.41,0:27:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得为他做出最好的选择\N{\fs12}We have got to do what is best for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.88,0:27:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他最需要的是关心和爱  不是愤怒\N{\fs12}And what is best for him is attention and love, not anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.08,0:27:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他还只是个孩子\N{\fs12}He's just a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.05,0:28:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们谈崩了\N{\fs12}That didn't go very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.58,0:28:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他不同意\N{\fs12}He won't agree to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.82,0:28:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.51,0:28:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是希望走法律的途径\N{\fs12}I still want to take this to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.46,0:28:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs12}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.31,0:28:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,至少\N{\fs12}At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.17,0:28:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我的儿子知道  妈妈真的努力做到最好了\N{\fs12}I want my son to know, at least, that I tried to do what I felt was best.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.75,0:28:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这本\N{\fs12}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.64,0:28:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\N{\fs12}Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.48,0:28:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.63,0:28:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我前夫很有权势\N{\fs12}My ex-husband is a powerful guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.28,0:28:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.31,0:28:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你不懂  他真的很有权势\N{\fs12}No. I mean, he's a powerful guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.03,0:28:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个律师  他这个人心狠手辣\N{\fs12}He's a lawyer, and he's very tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.27,0:28:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以解决\N{\fs12}Well, I can handle myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.35,0:28:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,会有很多人跟他一起来\N{\fs12}He'll bring a lot of people with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.20,0:28:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他会表现得很友好  他是他会嘲弄也会很傲慢\N{\fs12}He'll act kindly, but he'll be derisive and condescending.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.92,0:28:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.04,0:29:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他会把我说成另外一个人\N{\fs12}He'll make me out to be someone I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.92,0:29:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs12}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.24,0:29:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定会提到我一直和\N{\fs12}He might bring up the fact that I've struggled with--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.02,0:29:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和什么\N{\fs12}With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.10,0:29:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,药物和酒精作斗争的事\N{\fs12}Pills. Alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.94,0:29:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能会提到\N{\fs12}He might bring that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.64,0:29:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不相关的事  法官只会在乎\N{\fs12}lt's irrelevant. The judge is only concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.33,0:29:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你的妹妹和你的前夫\N{\fs12}with your sister and your ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.81,0:29:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,对  是的\N{\fs12}Right. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.92,0:29:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮  抱歉  路上堵  停车又花了点时间\N{\fs12}Anne! I'm so sorry. Tramic and parking.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.76,0:29:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  尼克\N{\fs12}Oh, hi, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.27,0:29:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,丽兹阿姨\N{\fs12}Aunt Liz?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.51,0:29:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮  听我说  我觉得我做不到\N{\fs12}Anne, listen, I don't think I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.20,0:29:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 丽兹  - 我爱你的儿子  我真的爱他\N{\fs12}- Liz. - I love your son. I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.95,0:29:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得现在不是时候\N{\fs12}But I don't think now's the time to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.74,0:29:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你之前答应我了  - 我确实说了\N{\fs12}- You said that you would. - I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.53,0:29:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我觉得你前夫是\N{\fs12}Because I think your husband is...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.74,0:29:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意你之前说的很多事情  但是  安妮\N{\fs12}I agree with a lot of the things you say but, Anne,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.45,0:29:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你这么做是为了报复他\N{\fs12}I think you're doing this to get back at him,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.98,0:29:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是因为你认为这样是为了你儿子好\N{\fs12}not because you think that this is best for your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.78,0:29:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.57,0:30:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.31,0:30:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我儿子要跟着他爸爸了\N{\fs12}So, he goes to live with his dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.93,0:30:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.69,0:30:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那我回去帮他收拾行李吧\N{\fs12}Well, I better go get him packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.60,0:30:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.14,0:30:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我希望他今晚就走  - 为什么\N{\fs12}- I want him to go tonight. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.83,0:30:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不想让他跟我一起经历这些\N{\fs12}Because I don't want him to go through this with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.20,0:30:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至还不知道这件事\N{\fs12}He doesn't even know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.06,0:30:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.17,0:30:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  他也得现在就走了  早点去适应那边\N{\fs12}Well, he'll just have to go now and get used to where he'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.49,0:30:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮  他还不知道\N{\fs12}Anne, he doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.77,0:30:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的帮助\N{\fs12}Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.20,0:30:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我必须得这么做\N{\fs12}But this is the way it's gotta be.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.73,0:30:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生呢\N{\fs12}Where's Mr. Fallin?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.20,0:30:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我代替他出庭  法官大人\N{\fs12}I'm filling in for him, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.70,0:30:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.54,0:30:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,亨德里克斯小姐\N{\fs12}Miss Hendricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.60,0:30:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你断绝了和你前男友的往来\N{\fs12}I see you've stopped all contact with your former boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.05,0:30:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,修完了父母育儿课程  找到了一份工作\N{\fs12}have completed your parenting classes, have a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.38,0:31:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,家庭调查的结果也很不错\N{\fs12}Home study looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.88,0:31:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.98,0:31:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我没有看到你的\N{\fs12}I don't, however, see a certificate of completion
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.83,0:31:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,戒毒康复的证书\N{\fs12}for your drug rehabilitation program.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.07,0:31:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿到了  我完成了\N{\fs12}I took it. I finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.89,0:31:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是  但是我没有看到\N{\fs12}Yes, but I don't see proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.19,0:31:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,阿切尔小姐\N{\fs12}Miss Archer?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.95,0:31:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我恐怕  法官大人  我没有\N{\fs12}Um, I'm afraid, Your Honor, I don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.34,0:31:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我三天前就把证书给了那个该死的律师\N{\fs12}I gave it to that damn lawyer! Three days ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.94,0:31:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我在周五给了他\N{\fs12}I gave it to him on Friday!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.57,0:31:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  亨德里克斯小姐  我必须看到一张签过字的表格\N{\fs12}I'm sorry, Miss Hendricks, but I need to see a signed form before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.29,0:31:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  我宝贝女儿已经在那个烂地方住了快半年了\N{\fs12}Judge, my baby girl has been living in a crappy hellhole for almost six months--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.50,0:31:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿切尔女士  - 我只想让她跟我回家啊\N{\fs12}- Miss Archer. - And I just want to get her home to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.12,0:31:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 请你坐下  - 阿切尔小姐  管管你的当事人\N{\fs12}- You need to sit down! - Miss Archer, your client!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.23,0:31:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,阿切尔小姐\N{\fs12}Miss Archer!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.57,0:31:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我要看到证书\N{\fs12}Bring me the form.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.33,0:31:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不懂你的孩子被夺走是一种什么样的感觉\N{\fs12}You don't understand what it's like to have your baby taken from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.59,0:31:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.64,0:31:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,本来就是今天的\N{\fs12}It was supposed to be today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.45,0:32:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我把家里布置得好好的  我的朋友\N{\fs12}I had the house all done up and my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.19,0:32:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,本来就是今天的\N{\fs12}It was supposed to be today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.95,0:32:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.32,0:32:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我对我所做的感到抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm sorry...what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.91,0:32:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是\N{\fs12}I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.73,0:32:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我三言两句就能解决的事情\N{\fs12}lt's not really something I can make go away with words, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.15,0:32:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是对他又感觉\N{\fs12}I just really felt something for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.85,0:32:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很强烈的感觉\N{\fs12}I felt a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.31,0:32:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来过这样的感受  从来没有\N{\fs12}That doesn't happen for me, that doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.53,0:32:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs12}And I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.36,0:32:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拿到了  - 太好了\N{\fs12}- I got it. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.08,0:32:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在哪儿找到的  - 它就在厨房的柜台上\N{\fs12}- Where'd you find it? - It was on the counter in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.06,0:33:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼古拉斯在吗  - 他不在  但是\N{\fs12}- Was Nicholas there? - No. No, he wasn't, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.56,0:33:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  看上去挺好的  所以\N{\fs12}I mean, it all looked good, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.19,0:33:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.98,0:33:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我们把这事做完吧\N{\fs12}Well, let's get this thing done.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.64,0:33:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.01,0:33:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  很抱歉耽误大家这么长时间  大家都坐吧\N{\fs12}All right. Sorry for the delay. Why don't you have a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.53,0:33:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让他记着我病恹恹  日渐消瘦的样子\N{\fs12}I don't want him to remember me sick, wasting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.73,0:33:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能就这样把他赶出去吧\N{\fs12}You can't just kick him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.98,0:33:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他不应该这样面对这件事  - 他必须这样\N{\fs12}- He shouldn't have to face this. - He'll want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.72,0:33:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你就把他送去学校\N{\fs12}So you're just gonna drive off to the school
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.51,0:33:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然后告诉他你不能再陪伴他了吗\N{\fs12}and tell him that he can't be around you anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.27,0:33:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这样对大家都好  - 都好吗\N{\fs12}- It's for the best. - For the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.65,0:33:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 安妮  问问他他想要什么吧\N{\fs12}- Yes. - Anne, just ask him what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.86,0:33:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他不知道  - 他知道\N{\fs12}- He doesn't know. - He does!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.36,0:33:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不  他不知道  - 他想跟你在一起\N{\fs12}- No, he doesn't! - He wants to stay with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.47,0:33:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他想知道  他有帮助你\N{\fs12}He wants to know that he's helped you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.33,0:33:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他不应该面对这一切  他不是那种孩子\N{\fs12}He shouldn't have to face this. He is not that kind of child.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.02,0:33:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经和他爸爸很生疏了\N{\fs12}He's already so removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.65,0:33:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我让他继续待在这里  情况会更糟糕的\N{\fs12}lf I let him stay, it'll only make him worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.12,0:33:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,事实不是你想的那样的\N{\fs12}You don't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.43,0:33:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有办法知道某天他一觉醒来躺在他爸爸的家里是什么样\N{\fs12}You don't know what it's like for him to suddenly wake up in his father's house
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.09,0:33:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,直到你卧床不起  他才能来看你\N{\fs12}and to not see you again until you're too sick to object to his being there!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.57,0:33:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他应该习惯跟他爸爸待在一起\N{\fs12}He should get used to being with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.62,0:33:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他还有那么长时间跟他爸爸在一起  但是陪你的时间只有几个月了\N{\fs12}He has the rest of his life for that. He only has a few months left with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.73,0:34:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮  我很抱歉好吗\N{\fs12}Anne. Anne, I'm sorry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.87,0:34:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能听我说\N{\fs12}Will you please listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.79,0:34:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮  求你了\N{\fs12}Anne, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.03,0:34:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,让他跟你待在一起吧  直到他准备好了\N{\fs12}Just let him stay with you until he's ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.98,0:34:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我要这么做\N{\fs12}Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.25,0:34:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他会变的\N{\fs12}Because he'll change.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.10,0:34:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他会变成一个\N{\fs12}He'll end up...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.70,0:34:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,变成什么  尼克\N{\fs12}He'll end up what, Nick?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.71,0:34:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我这是为了他好\N{\fs12}lt's for his own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.96,0:34:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要走\N{\fs12}Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.52,0:35:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了  求你了  求你了  不要走\N{\fs12}Please. Please. Please, don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.08,0:35:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮你的  尼克\N{\fs12}I'll still help you, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.72,0:35:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了  求你了  别走\N{\fs12}Please. Please don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.12,0:35:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说了  我会帮你的\N{\fs12}I'll help you, like I said I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.79,0:35:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,别走\N{\fs12}Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.12,0:35:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.88,0:35:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒  尼克\N{\fs12}Nick! Nick!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.53,0:35:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs12}lt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.52,0:35:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  尼克  醒醒   没事了\N{\fs12}Nick! Nick! It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.73,0:35:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃了美人\N{\fs12}I took beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.65,0:35:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克  你吃了什么  尼克  尼克\N{\fs12}Nick, what'd you take? Nick! Nick!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.62,0:35:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们带你出去  我们会照顾好你的\N{\fs12}We're gonna get you outta here. We'll take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.66,0:35:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧  尼克  我们走\N{\fs12}Come on, Nick. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.61,0:36:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我们走\N{\fs12}All right. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.25,0:36:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 嗨\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.44,0:36:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样了\N{\fs12}How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.31,0:36:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝色梦幻是吧\N{\fs12}Blue Mystic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.25,0:36:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.79,0:36:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗑太多了吧\N{\fs12}Too much of a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.71,0:36:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs12}Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.73,0:36:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为你做了什么\N{\fs12}What'd they do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.46,0:36:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  他们就给了我一些\N{\fs12}You know, they just gave me some...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.07,0:36:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,托住我的头  聊了聊\N{\fs12}Held my hand, talked me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.71,0:36:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢他们没有报警\N{\fs12}Nice of them not to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.33,0:36:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.80,0:36:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我代理这家医院\N{\fs12}Well, I do represent the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.20,0:36:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我都忘了\N{\fs12}Right. I forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.70,0:36:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,至少以前有\N{\fs12}At least I used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.22,0:36:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我打电话告诉你爸了\N{\fs12}I called your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.90,0:37:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也跟露露说了\N{\fs12}And I spoke to Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.20,0:37:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们不要过来了  我送你回家\N{\fs12}Told them not to come down here, that I'd take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.33,0:37:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.67,0:37:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你以后慢慢谢\N{\fs12}Well, we'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.70,0:37:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你嗑的那种药  蓝色梦幻\N{\fs12}That drug you took, Blue Mystic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.19,0:37:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 为什么\N{\fs12}- Right. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.39,0:37:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.13,0:37:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是这种药\N{\fs12}Why that drug?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.66,0:37:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有个人  他告诉我\N{\fs12}This guy, he, uh... he told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.29,0:37:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他说这个药嗑了之后感觉无与伦比\N{\fs12}He said it was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.73,0:37:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.36,0:37:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是这样  无与伦比\N{\fs12}And it was. Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.91,0:37:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但是只维持了一段时间\N{\fs12}It was...for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.82,0:37:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,致幻剂  我记得那种感觉\N{\fs12}Hallucinogens. I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.60,0:37:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,无与伦比\N{\fs12}lncredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.19,0:38:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事了  阿尔文  谢谢你  你可以回家了\N{\fs12}I'm fine, Alvin. Thank you. You can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.84,0:38:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道\N{\fs12}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.69,0:38:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在已经4点了  我也很累了\N{\fs12}lt's 4 in the morning, and I'm pretty tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.15,0:38:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是  肯定很累了\N{\fs12}Right. I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.51,0:38:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.98,0:38:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  你应该\N{\fs12}So, uh, you should...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.96,0:38:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,回家了吧\N{\fs12}Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.34,0:38:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.01,0:38:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不要喝杯茶\N{\fs12}Would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.62,0:38:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不用\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.34,0:38:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\fs12}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.69,0:38:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我要\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.22,0:38:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话\N{\fs12}lf you wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.33,0:38:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.61,0:38:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,外面真的太冷了\N{\fs12}Cold as hell out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.65,0:38:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨  - 嗨\N{\fs12}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.45,0:38:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fs12}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.75,0:39:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都坐吧  坐下谈一谈\N{\fs12}why don't we sit down and have a little talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.51,0:39:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我要做什么\N{\fs12}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.57,0:39:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在那边  告诉他们你的名字\N{\fs12}Go over there and give them your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.59,0:39:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fs12}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.96,0:39:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.97,0:39:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨  我叫尼克·法林\N{\fs12}Hi, uh, my name is Nick Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.35,0:39:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要跟人谈一谈\N{\fs12}I wanted to talk to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.03,0:40:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我已经知道你的基本信息了\N{\fs12}Okay, I've got all your basic information.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.03,0:40:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.75,0:40:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有几个选择\N{\fs12}We've got a few options here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.57,0:40:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.40,0:40:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得我们需要承认你要去戒毒诊所\N{\fs12}I don't think we need to admit you for detox.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.83,0:40:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.27,0:40:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉我们在接下来的一个月都需要门诊治疗\N{\fs12}My feeling is we should start outpatient for the next 30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.10,0:40:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.92,0:40:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是每晚4个小时  每周五天\N{\fs12}That's four hours a night, five days a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.62,0:40:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.34,0:40:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你可以吗\N{\fs12}You think you can handle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.89,0:40:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.65,0:40:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fs12}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.12,0:40:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.81,0:40:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会帮你的  法林先生\N{\fs12}We're gonna help you, Mr. Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.24,0:40:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.39,0:40:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会尽全力帮你\N{\fs12}We will give you all the help you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.98,0:40:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.48,0:40:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,现在轮到你选择了  尼克\N{\fs12}lt's your turn, Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.81,0:40:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你准备好了  轮到你选择了\N{\fs12}lf you're ready, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.91,0:41:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,尼克\N{\fs12}Nick.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.70,0:41:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮塔·亨德里克斯需要你跟她去法庭\N{\fs12}Anita Hendricks needs you to take her to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.11,0:41:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.55,0:41:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她说她把戒毒康复的证书给你了\N{\fs12}And she said that she gave you her certificate for her drug rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.31,0:41:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,确实给我了  在我的办公室\N{\fs12}She did. It's in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.78,0:41:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  她非常生气\N{\fs12}Well, you know, she's pretty angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.22,0:41:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以也许你应该把证书给我  让我\N{\fs12}so maybe you could just give it to me and I'll--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.43,0:41:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  她是我的客户\N{\fs12}No, she's my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.93,0:41:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道  但是也许我可以  - 她是我的客户\N{\fs12}- I know, but maybe I could just-- - She's my client.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.79,0:41:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  亨德里克斯小姐  我知道我们今天中午12点要去法庭\N{\fs12}Okay, Miss Hendricks, I understand we have a 12:OO today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.41,0:41:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是吗\N{\fs12}Damn straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.17,0:41:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  进我办公室吧  我们把文件准备好\N{\fs12}Well, if you step into my office, we can get that form ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.02,0:41:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有什么话跟我说吗\N{\fs12}Don't you got something to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.22,0:41:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对  我有话说\N{\fs12}You're right, I do. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.09,0:41:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs12}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.96,0:41:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.98,0:41:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs12}All right, then.
